    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion was met at all five evaluated operating points.",
